<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-AO" data-theme="dark">
<head>
    <%- include('../../partials/head-meta', { title: 'Erro Interno no Servidor', moduleStyle: 'auth' }) %>
    <style>
        .error-page-wrapper {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #1a1a2e 0%, #0b0b12 100%);
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 10rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: -5px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(255, 59, 92, 0.4));
        }
        .error-message h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--text-main);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .error-message p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 550px;
            margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
        }
        .technical-details {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            text-align: left;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        .technical-details label {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .error-stack {
            font-family: 'Monaco', 'Consolas', monospace;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            max-height: 150px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .btn-retry {
            padding: 12px 35px;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-radius: 50px;
            background: var(--secondary-color);
            border: none;
            color: white;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(124, 77, 255, 0.3);
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .btn-retry:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            filter: brightness(1.2);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(124, 77, 255, 0.5);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-page-wrapper">
        <div class="container animate-up">
            <div class="error-code">500</div>
            
            <div class="mb-4">
                <i class="bi bi-cpu-fill text-danger" style="font-size: 5rem; opacity: 0.5;"></i>
            </div>

            <div class="error-message">
                <h1>Falha Crítica no Sistema</h1>
                <p>Detectamos uma instabilidade nos nossos servidores em Luanda. O núcleo de processamento encontrou uma excepção não tratada e a operação foi interrompida.</p>
                
                <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined' && error) { %>
                <div class="technical-details">
                    <label><i class="bi bi-terminal me-2"></i>Relatório de Erro para Devs</label>
                    <div class="error-stack">
                        <%= error %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <% } %>

                <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-center gap-3">
                    <button class="btn-retry" onclick="window.location.reload()">
                        <i class="bi bi-arrow-clockwise"></i> Tentar Novamente
                    </button>
                    <a href="/reports" class="btn-oc btn-oc-outline px-4">
                        <i class="bi bi-headset"></i> Contactar Suporte
                    </a>
                    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-oc btn-oc-outline px-4">
                        <i class="bi bi-house"></i> Início
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-5 pt-5 border-top border-secondary border-opacity-10">
                <div class="text-dim small">
                    Timestamp: <%= new Date().toISOString() %> | Server Node: Ang-01-LAD
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Core Scripts -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>